{"tid":1430441,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我係茶理史員工 觀塘有兩間分店 我要割𥱊","createTime":"2019-08-07T17:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T22:10:46.000Z","uid":264499,"like":97,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc85f57ce52f7636ba729d57cb871daecd64ddd","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:47:40.000Z","msg":"借fd ac代po<br />\n<br />\n啱先見到有巴打想抵制觀塘茶理史 <br />\n但首先<span style=\"font-size: large;\">歡塘有兩間分店</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">on9親中po嗰個 唔係近牛頭角站嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n因為見到有巴打comment 搞錯左兩間分店 希望大家唔好殺錯良店 事實上 我地員工都有響應罷工 而係某一日當示威者發夢經過我地鋪都有派免費茶(勿相認驚比人炒) 當我知道第二間分店po埋啲on9嘢自己都好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係講個好消息比大家 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">親中嗰間分店9月30號終止合約啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> 所以大家矛頭直指佢地啦 <br />\n<br />\n因為以我所知我地老闆甚至捐左大量物資比前線 係物資唔係餐卷 所以真係唔希望佢間鋪會因為分店嘅仆街行為受到牽連 當然啦 我只係員工 總公司嘅政治取態就唔知啦 總知大家加油 槍頭對出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fd1ba6c2a1fecb319e4f811aaed413b6b0d17a","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:48:29.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"afd9953784cbbcca523ca6428ef3e5d807100b08","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:48:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17e9a60aee36a19ac46961d4957a7178a6e0bf83","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:49:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"509a16bd9b87ad7d768b1177f1f507a8ded9cb7e","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:49:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd5d99efed29bf683223e9c7a8048095af3d0ff5","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4eed5fc192e4c266bbc22d3d44028f85c1c93640","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:49:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"595d6a63d2365b0ad8e5be640e6efe957655d859","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:49:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25158b661a8f7164c9362fc577bdce8ba3f26b8a","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:50:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4873f047b34b6aad4556ccb660eff0887c25153b","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:50:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bcf8f1511982fbf88d3d21d69e4cba980dfd11c","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:50:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d66715d1fa19366653bb7246c8d11f9174425bf","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:51:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49621406f3809e28af2591259bd3298c171c22de","tid":1430441,"uid":79611,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"近和樂村嗰間係咪茶理史???"},{"pid":"4d02ee58998714926e2318df4120c273c5d7395a","tid":1430441,"uid":264499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"49621406f3809e28af2591259bd3298c171c22de","tid":1430441,"uid":79611,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"近和樂村嗰間係咪茶理史???"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:57:59.000Z","msg":"親中有鐵棍個間係觀塘！觀塘！觀塘！協和街！協和街！嘅茶理史 <br />\n但牛頭角個間係馬蹄徑 之前豪大大個位 裕民坊隔離 近牛頭角地鐵站 唔好搞錯"},{"pid":"51b246538917aa0599d7a258baed74449e4d473e","tid":1430441,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:29:31.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意飲茶理史<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi